[src:transmission-line/alexander-stepanovich-popov] Popov received the very first radiogram using the device he invented", 1961.
[src:transmission-line/alexander-stepanovich-popov] With the support of the International Telecommunication Union (ITU) in Geneva from 5 to 9 October 2009, the World Exhibition “Telecommunication World 2009” was held (ITU Telecom World 2009).
[src:transmission-line/alexander-stepanovich-popov] Among the events was the opening of a plaque to A.
